latestPosts.caption:
I recently visted @thespraytanlounge I cannot get over HOW GOOD I FEEL! 🥺💖😩

I had a Teeth Whitening & Spray Tan combo (yes you can book these as a combo service)  I had such an amazing visit my providers made me feel like I was hanging with long time friends and every lady who walked in while I was there left smiling golden and stunning.

With summer almost here check out their Self Love Club this membership gets 50% off Spray Tans (unlimited per month) 25% off Teeth whitening services, 10% off retail  plus a free Birthday tan! 🫡🙂‍↔️💖 Best part it’s only $ 25/mo and waaaay better than your Netflix subscription.

#spraytan #spraytanning #pdxspraytan #pdxsmallbusiness #teethwhitening
